Weblink : https://github.com/megvii-model/HINet

HINet: Half Instance Normalization Network for Image Restoration


Installation
This implementation based on <a href="https://github.com/xinntao/BasicSR">BasicSR </a> which is a open source toolbox for image/video restoration tasks.




python 3.6.9
pytorch 1.5.1
cuda 10.1

